Supplementary Information 2 - Global annual average landings of Sharks MOU Annex I-listed species reported to FAO (2015-2019)

\(~\)

\(~\)

Each FAO area tab has two plots and a table representing the total landings of Sharks MOU Annex I-listed species reported to FAO.

All landings are reported as tonnes of live weight.

The first plot includes the top three nations reporting the highest landings, as can be seen in Figure 3 of the main document. The second plot represents a close up of the landings reported from the remaining nations, as it is seen at the fourth bar within the plots presented in Figure 3 of the main document. Note the scale between the two plots is different.

Colour of nations within plots indicate Sharks MOU and CMS Status: (Dark blue) Sharks MOU Signatory and CMS Party; (light blue) Sharks MOU Signatory only; (green) CMS Party only; (grey) range state. Note that not all colours may be present in any given plot.
